<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Documentation API - Port de Plaisance Russell</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 30px; }
        h1 { color: #1e3a5f; }
        h2 { color: #2e6da4; margin-top: 30px; }
        table { border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        th { background-color: #1e3a5f; color: white; padding: 10px; text-align: left; }
        td { padding: 8px 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; }
        tr:nth-child(even) { background-color: #f0f5fa; }
        .method { font-weight: bold; font-family: monospace; }
        .get { color: #27ae60; }
        .post { color: #2980b9; }
        .put { color: #e67e22; }
        .delete { color: #e74c3c; }
        .url { font-family: monospace; }
        .nav { margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .nav a { margin-right: 15px; color: #2e6da4; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="nav">
        <a href="/">Accueil</a>
        <a href="/dashboard">Dashboard</a>
    </div>

    <h1>Documentation de l'API</h1>
    <p>API REST du Port de Plaisance Russell. Toutes les routes (sauf <code>/auth/login</code>) nécessitent un token JWT dans le header <code>Authorization: Bearer &lt;token&gt;</code>.</p>

    <h2>Authentification</h2>
    <table>
        <tr>
            <th>Méthode</th>
            <th>Route</th>
            <th>Description</th>
            <th>Auth requise</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><span class="method post">POST</span></td>
            <td class="url">/auth/login</td>
            <td>Se connecter et obtenir un token JWT</td>
            <td>Non</td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <h2>Catways</h2>
    <table>
        <tr>
            <th>Méthode</th>
            <th>Route</th>
            <th>Description</th>
            <th>Auth requise</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><span class="method get">GET</span></td>
            <td class="url">/catways</td>
            <td>Lister tous les catways</td>
            <td>Oui</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><span class="method get">GET</span></td>
            <td class="url">/catways/:id</td>
            <td>Obtenir les détails d'un catway</td>
            <td>Oui</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><span class="method post">POST</span></td>
            <td class="url">/catways</td>
            <td>Créer un nouveau catway</td>
            <td>Oui</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><span class="method put">PUT</span></td>
            <td class="url">/catways/:id</td>
            <td>Modifier l'état d'un catway (catwayState uniquement)</td>
            <td>Oui</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><span class="method delete">DELETE</span></td>
            <td class="url">/catways/:id</td>
            <td>Supprimer un catway</td>
            <td>Oui</td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <h2>Réservations</h2>
    <table>
        <tr>
            <th>Méthode</th>
            <th>Route</th>
            <th>Description</th>
            <th>Auth requise</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><span class="method get">GET</span></td>
            <td class="url">/catways/:id/reservations</td>
            <td>Lister toutes les réservations d'un catway</td>
            <td>Oui</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><span class="method post">POST</span></td>
            <td class="url">/catways/:id/reservations</td>
            <td>Créer une réservation sur un catway</td>
            <td>Oui</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><span class="method get">GET</span></td>
            <td class="url">/catways/:id/reservations/:reservationId</td>
            <td>Détails d'une réservation</td>
            <td>Oui</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><span class="method put">PUT</span></td>
            <td class="url">/catways/:id/reservations/:reservationId</td>
            <td>Modifier une réservation</td>
            <td>Oui</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><span class="method delete">DELETE</span></td>
            <td class="url">/catways/:id/reservations/:reservationId</td>
            <td>Supprimer une réservation</td>
            <td>Oui</td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <h2>Utilisateurs</h2>
    <table>
        <tr>
            <th>Méthode</th>
            <th>Route</th>
            <th>Description</th>
            <th>Auth requise</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><span class="method get">GET</span></td>
            <td class="url">/users</td>
            <td>Lister tous les utilisateurs</td>
            <td>Oui</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><span class="method get">GET</span></td>
            <td class="url">/users/:email</td>
            <td>Détails d'un utilisateur</td>
            <td>Oui</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><span class="method post">POST</span></td>
            <td class="url">/users</td>
            <td>Créer un utilisateur</td>
            <td>Oui</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><span class="method put">PUT</span></td>
            <td class="url">/users/:email</td>
            <td>Modifier un utilisateur</td>
            <td>Oui</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><span class="method delete">DELETE</span></td>
            <td class="url">/users/:email</td>
            <td>Supprimer un utilisateur</td>
            <td>Oui</td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <h2>Exemples de requêtes</h2>
    <h3>Login</h3>
    <pre>POST /auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "user@example.com",
    "password": "motdepasse"
}</pre>

    <h3>Requête authentifiée</h3>
    <pre>GET /catways
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...</pre>
</body>
</html>
